<!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
<section class="container py-5">
    <h1 class="text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-muted">Last updated: March 2025</p>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h4>1. Introduction</h4>
        <p>Welcome to the <strong>Appoinment Management System</strong>. Your privacy and security are our top priorities. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data.</p>

        <h4>2. Information We Collect</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, contact details</li>
            <li><strong>Medical & Appointment Data:</strong> Patient records and appointment details (Doctors & Staff only).</li>
            <li><strong>System Usage Data:</strong> Logins, access history, and activities for security monitoring.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>3. How We Use Your Data</h4>
        <p>We use your data for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Managing staff, appointments, and patient records efficiently.</li>
            <li>Ensuring security and compliance with healthcare policies.</li>
            <li>Providing a seamless user experience.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="text-danger">4. Patient Data Confidentiality</h4>
        <p><strong>All staff members must strictly follow patient confidentiality rules:</strong></p>
        <ul class="text-danger">
            <li>Patient data should only be accessed for official purposes.</li>
            <li><strong>No sharing of patient information</strong> with unauthorized individuals.</li>
            <li>Failure to comply may result in disciplinary action.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>5. Data Security Measures</h4>
        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect user and patient data, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Secure database encryption for sensitive data.</li>
            <li>Multi-level access control to restrict unauthorized access.</li>
            <li>Regular security audits and updates.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>6. Your Rights & Responsibilities</h4>
        <p>As a user, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Request access to your personal data.</li>
            <li>Update or correct your account information.</li>
            <li>Report any security concerns to the admin team.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>7. Changes to This Policy</h4>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy as needed. Any significant changes will be communicated to all users.</p>

        <h4>8. Contact Us</h4>
        <p>If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact our **Support Team**.</p>
    </div>
</section>